text: Kevin John Wickham (21 July 1939 - 4 July 2020) was an Australian rower. He competed as coxswain at the 1964 Summer Olympics. Wickham died on 4 July 2020, aged 80. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:1939 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Olympians for Australia Category:Sportspeople from Victoria (Australia)
